696
00:45:41,840 --> 00:45:43,980
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, i sad odjednom ja ne kažem,

697
00:45:43,980 --> 00:45:45,639
[SPEAKER_00] ona kad se nam malo smirila,

698
00:45:45,639 --> 00:45:46,739
