699
00:45:46,739 --> 00:45:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] dobro, upravo ste,

700
00:45:48,380 --> 00:45:51,380
[SPEAKER_00] što mi možemo čovjeku napraviti?

701
00:45:51,380 --> 00:45:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] Da, dobro ste rekli,

702
00:45:53,880 --> 00:45:54,639
[SPEAKER_00] da, okej,

703
00:45:54,639 --> 00:45:56,320
[SPEAKER_00] diže se ona i ode.

704
00:45:56,320 --> 00:45:58,900
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je sad, mislim,

705
00:45:58,900 --> 00:45:59,699
[SPEAKER_00] dobro, okej,

706
00:45:59,699 --> 00:46:01,619
[SPEAKER_00] dođe ona za deset minuta

707
00:46:01,619 --> 00:46:03,800
