708
00:46:03,800 --> 00:46:05,260
[SPEAKER_00] šta već ima puno papira.

709
00:46:05,260 --> 00:46:07,760
[SPEAKER_00] Rekla sam ja,

710
00:46:07,760 --> 00:46:10,159
[SPEAKER_00] nema tu njega od dve i pete,

711
00:46:10,159 --> 00:46:11,420
