750
00:47:11,119 --> 00:47:11,980
[SPEAKER_00] kažem Bogu hvala,

751
00:47:11,980 --> 00:47:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu hvala.

752
00:47:12,599 --> 00:47:13,099
